{"tid":1417173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非回合]聽我講，我哋要繼續打民意戰","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:09:47.000Z","uid":225916,"like":75,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7e38af0dfbaf2bc8a3c7b138b10ad552ef3790","tid":1417173,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"今日 打得好成功<br />\n打游擊戰 根本係勇武嘅極致<br />\n但問題係 我哋真係打得太成功啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋將市民對我哋嘅恐懼無限放大<br />\n好多鋪頭怕被人圍所以早收鋪，咁落去個問題係<br />\n佢哋好順理成章咁將件事<span style=\"color: red;\">推返落我哋度</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得暫時 要拆交通同阻地鐵 都係停一停先<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(唔反對圍狗屋，因為影響唔到班港豬)</span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以試一次咁打<br />\n18區全部落區宣傳 0衝擊 全部人冷靜少少去說服班港豬<br />\n利用羊群心理 其實唔難搞掂佢哋<br />\n最重要係將個矛頭指返去政府度就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n因為林鄭想將件事推落示威者同黑警衝突上<br />\n我哋就應該直接指責<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭漠視民意 </span></span><br />\n強調我哋係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">逼不得已</span></span><br />\n已經用盡辦法令政府回應 <br />\n得到嘅係4隻字 壽終正寢"},{"pid":"68f58ed62e15346b2590c4d0c26937ab22ac5354","tid":1417173,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d5fb5404aead4660aacd2fc29b633e2eb271519","tid":1417173,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"199156367ace2771a2cf4de70976932f2c3d5c45","tid":1417173,"uid":257422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:09:16.000Z","msg":"和理非請你永遠記住<br />\n&quot;不割蓆&quot;唔係叫你要認同哂所有抗爭手段，你絕對可以隨時提出意見；<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;不割蓆&quot; 意思係叫你就算點都好，都唔好離隊！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線亦請聆聽後勸意見，深思過先選擇行動，因為你一到左前線就無人阻到你！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;絕不放棄，抗爭到底，直到勝利&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n[ 溫故知新！] 成日話&quot;不割蓆&quot;, 都想大家深入明白咩叫&quot;不割蓆&quot;先！！(利申：不割)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"38ddb034d658d6fdca868a2603d6b152cb940945","tid":1417173,"uid":222190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001215_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001215_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=fb386f16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001216_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001216_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=43ced1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001217_204fd6f27813ec488a814ee7dd366cf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001217_204fd6f27813ec488a814ee7dd366cf7.png&h=eff8692e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001218_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001218_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png&h=204a3a0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64a4d146364b095bfba10f6f131ab3b6067f1a2a","tid":1417173,"uid":239313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68a2c9564ce311696deb936e48cfb885f5f395f1","tid":1417173,"uid":225916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"大家打得太靚 <br />\n我相信再過冇耐，我哋可以癱瘓完仲可以0被捕<br />\n<br />\n但確實係 再咁打落去<br />\n班港豬真係信tvb以為我哋係暴民<br />\n好難令佢哋企過我哋哩邊<br />\n因為同佢哋差距太大<br />\n就好似早幾日有巴打用心理學講<br />\n哩班人 將示威者叫做 &ldquo;佢哋&rdquo;<br />\n將大家分類為唔同嘅人<br />\n所以大家要話俾佢哋知<br />\n我哋都係香港人"},{"pid"