呀 大陸真係好黑暗 我都唔想香港變成咁<br />\n仲叫我哋小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e36abdb24c492e6e5c3aeec87b9d1185a2a156b","tid":1417173,"uid":225916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:28:45.000Z","msg":"將文宣推為 一對一/一對多式服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個區每個人  逐個逐個去講解<br />\n有唔明講到明<br />\n如果點講都唔聽 唔好屌，反而要叫佢哋:<br />\n<br />\n點都好，警察唔會保護市民，大家最緊要小心啲<br />\n<br />\n可以用關心形式去打動佢哋"},{"pid":"711e55d62df482be7d4828e8f4d87d18c3269ffe","tid":1417173,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"推 好撚攰都要推"},{"pid":"6b2a156deec6674537ac713fef62cdad13ecab54","tid":1417173,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:29:46.000Z","msg":"目標0被捕"}]}